微软研究院博客 - 微软研究院 https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/ 2024 年 1 月 31 日星期三 20:54:21 +0000 en-US每小时1 https://wordpress.org/?v=6.4.2
你的故事是什么：伊万·塔舍夫https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/whats-your-story-ivan-tashev/Alyssa Hughes Thu, 01 Feb 2024 14:00:00 +0000Research Blog https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/?p=1000779 <p>合作伙伴软件架构师 Ivan Tashev 讲述了如何将他在音频信号处理方面的专业知识应用到 Kinect 等 Microsoft 产品的音频组件的设计和研究中，并分享了对他可以控制的事物的关注如何推动了职业成功。</p><p><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/whats-your-story-ivan-tashev/">您的故事是什么：Ivan Tashev</a>这篇文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research">Microsoft Research</a>上。</p> ; 
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1400" height="788" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_T_WYS_Hero_Feature_1400x788.png" alt="Ivan Tashev 与 Microsoft Research Podcast 徽标的照片" class="wp-image-1000800" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_T_WYS_Hero_Feature_1400x788.png 1400w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_T_WYS_Hero_Feature_1400x788-300x169.png 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_T_WYS_Hero_Feature_1400x788-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_T_WYS_Hero_Feature_1400x788-768x432.png 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_T_WYS_Hero_Feature_1400x788-1066x600.png 1066w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_T_WYS_Hero_Feature_1400x788-655x368.png 655w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_T_WYS_Hero_Feature_1400x788-343x193.png 343w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_T_WYS_Hero_Feature_1400x788-240x135.png 240w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_T_WYS_Hero_Feature_1400x788-640x360.png 640w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_T_WYS_Hero_Feature_1400x788-960x540.png 960w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_T_WYS_Hero_Feature_1400x788-1280x720.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /></figure><div class="wp-block-msr-podcast-container"><iframe src="https://player.blubrry.com/?podcast_id=128560259&modern=1" class="podcast-player" frameborder="0" height="160px" width="100%" scrolling="no" title="播客播放器"></iframe></div><p>在 Microsoft Research 播客系列<em>“你的故事是什么”</em>中，Johannes Gehrke 探讨了帮助重塑世界的技术和科学进步背后的<em>人物</em>。 Gehrke 是一位系统专家，在 Microsoft 工作了 10 年，横跨研究和产品领域，他与公司研究社区的成员讨论了他们工作的动力以及他们如何取得今天的成就。</p><p>合作伙伴软件架构师 Ivan Tashev 在音频信号处理方面的专业知识为 Kinect、Teams 和 HoloLens 等 Microsoft 产品的音频组件的设计和研究做出了贡献。在这一集中，塔舍夫讨论了数学奥林匹克竞赛的第一名如何激发了他对拍摄电影的终生热情；一次展示尖端项目的公司活动如何促使他从产品转向研究；以及他在 Microsoft 工作 25 多年的时间里，专注于自己控制范围内的事情是如何帮助他取得成功的。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1600" height="462" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_Through_The_Years_Banner.png" alt="伊万·塔舍夫一生的照片" class="wp-image-1000803" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_Through_The_Years_Banner.png 1600w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_Through_The_Years_Banner-300x87.png 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_Through_The_Years_Banner-1024x296.png 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_Through_The_Years_Banner-768x222.png 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_Through_The_Years_Banner-1536x444.png 1536w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2024/01/Ivan_Through_The_Years_Banner-240x69.png 240w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></figure><div class="wp-block-group msr-pattern-link-list is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"><hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/><h2 class="wp-block-heading h5" id="learn-more-1">了解更多：</h2><ul class="list-unstyled"><li><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/ivantash/">微软研究院的 Ivan Tashev</a></li><li> <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/publication/distributed-meetings-a-meeting-capture-and-broadcasting-system/">分布式会议：会议捕获和广播系统</a><br>出版，2002 年 12 月</li><li><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/research-collection-the-unseen-history-of-audio-and-acoustics-research-at-microsoft/">研究集：微软音频和声学研究不为人知的历史</a><br>微软研究院博客，2020 年 8 月</li></ul></div><section class="wp-block-msr-subscribe-to-podcast subscribe-to-podcast"><div class="subscribe-to-podcast_